            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Jeremiah.31:27-32:44",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2031%3A27-32%3A44%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_27%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20day%20is%20coming%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bwhen%20I%20will%20greatly%20increase%20the%20human%20population%20and%20the%20number%20of%20animals%20here%20in%20Israel%20and%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_28%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20past%20I%20deliberately%20uprooted%20and%20tore%20down%20this%20nation.%20I%20overthrew%20it%2C%20destroyed%20it%2C%20and%20brought%20disaster%20upon%20it.%20But%20in%20the%20future%20I%20will%20just%20as%20deliberately%20plant%20it%20and%20build%20it%20up.%20I%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_29%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20people%20will%20no%20longer%20quote%20this%20proverb%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x2018%3BThe%20parents%20have%20eaten%20sour%20grapes%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20their%20children%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mouths%20pucker%20at%20the%20taste.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_30%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20people%20will%20die%20for%20their%20own%20sins%26%23x2014%3Bthose%20who%20eat%20the%20sour%20grapes%20will%20be%20the%20ones%20whose%20mouths%20will%20pucker.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_31%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20day%20is%20coming%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bwhen%20I%20will%20make%20a%20new%20covenant%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20and%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_32%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20covenant%20will%20not%20be%20like%20the%20one%20I%20made%20with%20their%20ancestors%20when%20I%20took%20them%20by%20the%20hand%20and%20brought%20them%20out%20of%20the%20land%20of%20Egypt.%20They%20broke%20that%20covenant%2C%20though%20I%20loved%20them%20as%20a%20husband%20loves%20his%20wife%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_33%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20this%20is%20the%20new%20covenant%20I%20will%20make%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20after%20those%20days%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20put%20my%20instructions%20deep%20within%20them%2C%20and%20I%20will%20write%20them%20on%20their%20hearts.%20I%20will%20be%20their%20God%2C%20and%20they%20will%20be%20my%20people.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_34%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20they%20will%20not%20need%20to%20teach%20their%20neighbors%2C%20nor%20will%20they%20need%20to%20teach%20their%20relatives%2C%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20should%20know%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%20For%20everyone%2C%20from%20the%20least%20to%20the%20greatest%2C%20will%20know%20me%20already%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20I%20will%20forgive%20their%20wickedness%2C%20and%20I%20will%20never%20again%20remember%20their%20sins.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_35%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20provides%20the%20sun%20to%20light%20the%20day%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20moon%20and%20stars%20to%20light%20the%20night%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20who%20stirs%20the%20sea%20into%20roaring%20waves.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHis%20name%20is%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20this%20is%20what%20he%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_36%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20as%20likely%20to%20reject%20my%20people%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eas%20I%20am%20to%20abolish%20the%20laws%20of%20nature!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_37%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BJust%20as%20the%20heavens%20cannot%20be%20measured%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20foundations%20of%20the%20earth%20cannot%20be%20explored%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eso%20I%20will%20not%20consider%20casting%20them%20away%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20the%20evil%20they%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_38%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2238%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E38%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20day%20is%20coming%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bwhen%20all%20Jerusalem%20will%20be%20rebuilt%20for%20me%2C%20from%20the%20Tower%20of%20Hananel%20to%20the%20Corner%20Gate.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_39%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2239%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E39%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20measuring%20line%20will%20be%20stretched%20out%20over%20the%20hill%20of%20Gareb%20and%20across%20to%20Goah.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_31_40%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2240%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E40%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20the%20entire%20area%26%23x2014%3Bincluding%20the%20graveyard%20and%20ash%20dump%20in%20the%20valley%2C%20and%20all%20the%20fields%20out%20to%20the%20Kidron%20Valley%20on%20the%20east%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Horse%20Gate%26%23x2014%3Bwill%20be%20holy%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20The%20city%20will%20never%20again%20be%20captured%20or%20destroyed.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJeremiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Land%20Purchase%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20following%20message%20came%20to%20Jeremiah%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20the%20tenth%20year%20of%20the%20reign%20of%20Zedekiah%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E32%3A1a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20tenth%20year%20of%20Zedekiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%20and%20the%20eighteenth%20year%20of%20Nebuchadnezzar%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%20was%20587%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20king%20of%20Judah.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20eighteenth%20year%20of%20the%20reign%20of%20King%20Nebuchadnezzar.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E32%3A1b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3ENebuchadrezzar%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Nebuchadnezzar%3B%20also%20in%2032%3A28.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EJerusalem%20was%20then%20under%20siege%20from%20the%20Babylonian%20army%2C%20and%20Jeremiah%20was%20imprisoned%20in%20the%20courtyard%20of%20the%20guard%20in%20the%20royal%20palace.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Zedekiah%20had%20put%20him%20there%2C%20asking%20why%20he%20kept%20giving%20this%20prophecy%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20am%20about%20to%20hand%20this%20city%20over%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%2C%20and%20he%20will%20take%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Zedekiah%20will%20be%20captured%20by%20the%20Babylonians%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E32%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EChaldeans%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2032%3A5%2C%2024%2C%2025%2C%2028%2C%2029%2C%2043.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20taken%20to%20meet%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%20face%20to%20face.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20will%20take%20Zedekiah%20to%20Babylon%2C%20and%20I%20will%20deal%20with%20him%20there%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%26%23x2018%3BIf%20you%20fight%20against%20the%20Babylonians%2C%20you%20will%20never%20succeed.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20that%20time%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sent%20me%20a%20message.%20He%20said%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYour%20cousin%20Hanamel%20son%20of%20Shallum%20will%20come%20and%20say%20to%20you%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BBuy%20my%20field%20at%20Anathoth.%20By%20law%20you%20have%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20it%20before%20it%20is%20offered%20to%20anyone%20else.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_32_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2232%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20said%20he%20would%2C%20my%20cousin%20Hanamel%20came%20and%20visited%20me%20in%20the%20prison.%20He%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPl